∀ (n : ℕ), n ≥ 1 → let f : ℕ → ℕ := fun n => ∑ i in Finset.range n, Nat.factorial (i + 1) in
  let P : ℕ → ℕ := fun x => x + 3 in
  let Q : ℕ → ℕ := fun x => -x - 2 in
  f (n + 2) = P n * f (n + 1) + Q n * f n
∀ (n : ℕ), 1 ≤ n → ∃ P Q : ℕ → ℤ, ∀ f : ℕ → ℤ, f (n + 2) = P n * f (n + 1) + Q n * f n
∀ {n : ℕ}, 1 ≤ n → (let P x := x + 3; Q x := -x - 2 in f (n + 2) = P n * f (n + 1) + Q n * f n)

∀ (n : ℕ), 1 ≤ n → let f : ℕ → ℕ := λ n, Finset.sum (Finset.range n.succ) Nat.factorial in
  f (n + 2) = (n + 3) * f (n + 1) + (-n - 2) * f n

∀ (n : ℕ), 1 ≤ n → ∃ (P Q : ℕ → ℤ), P n = n + 3 ∧ Q n = -n - 2 ∧
  (let f : ℕ → ℤ := λ n, ∑ i in Finset.range n, Nat.factorial i in f (n + 2) = P n * f (n + 1) + Q n * f n)

∀ (n : ℕ), 1 ≤ n → let f : ℕ → ℕ := λ n, (Finset.range n).sum (λ i, Nat.factorial (i + 1)) in
  f (n + 2) = (n + 3) * f (n + 1) + (-n - 2) * f n
